Tytthus insperatus
: 
Carvalho and Southwood 1955
: 31 (descrip., n. comb.); 
Carvalho 1958
: 157 (cat.); 
Henry and Wheeler 1988
: 458 (cat.); 
Schuh 1995
: 248 (cat.).

Described from Tucson (Pima County), Arizona, and later reported from Buckeye (Maricopa County), Arizona, and Calexico (Imperial County), California (
Carvalho and Southwood 1955
).
